[[File:Greel_Tree.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Greel tree forest]]
A '''greel tree''' was a type of [[Wikipedia:Tree|tree]] native to [[Pii III]] and [[Pii IV]], the only planets with the proper ecosystem to support the fastidious trees. The [[Greel Wood Logging Corporation]], based in the [[Pii system/Legends|Pii system]], maintained a monopoly on harvesting them. The crimson timber&mdash;[[Greel wood/Legends|greel wood]]&mdash;was in great demand as a luxury item. [[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton]] designed a [[FLR-series Logger Droid|logging droid]] to specifications for the Greel Wood Logging Corporation, which used them on the rolling hillsides of Pii III. They were apparently very expensive.<ref name="EGD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

